snippet.title: EDYN - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Check out gameplay, including customization options and more, from EDYN in this trailer for the upcoming MMO RTS game. EDYN launches into Early Access on Steam on November 21, 2024. Join the battle for EDYN, the ultimate multiplayer strategy game. Build settlements, command armies, and unify the realms in epic PvP warfare to etch your legacy into history.
